		<h3>18 Feb 2016, 'Between the Bullet and the Hole' (Plus Other Shorts) + Q&A at Whitechapel Gallery, London
		</h3>
		<p>
			Aura Satz presents the UK premiere of 'Between the Bullet and the Hole', her latest short film
			which examines the role of women in ballistic research, early computing and pattern perception
			in warfare. Presented alongside her works focusing on memory, notation, encryption and gender,
			the event also features an in conversation with special guests Morgan Quaintance and David
			Alan Grier.
		</p>
